<div>
  <h2 class="text-xl leading-6 font-medium text-gray-900">Account</h2>
  <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-500">
    GitHub is all we got for logging in for now. But do request us if you want some more ways :)
  </p>
</div>
<div class="relative mt-3">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="w-full border-t border-gray-300"></div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="mt-10">
  <div class="flex items-center shadow border rounded p-5">
    <div class="pr-3">
      <div class="mx-auto flex items-center justify-center h-12 w-12 rounded-full">
